name: Valerian cubes, Valerian toy, toy for cats, plush cubes, gift, cat toy, Crazy Cat Lady, unique
description: Each cube of valerian measures about 4x4x4cm, is made of cotton and filled with polyester OR organic quality spelt husk and 3g ground valerian root.Spelt husk is a pure natural product and seduces with its light crackling sound to wild romping and playing.If you want, you can pimp the toy for the tiger with a bell or crackling foil.In addition, each cube is a unique toy for your cat.Individually airtight welded. If you buy several valerian toys, they are sealed together to avoid unnecessary packaging waste.If you buy a toy, a cube will be sent by chance. You can also leave a color of your choice in the comment. We will then choose an appropriate cube. IMPORTANT! Valerian and toys with it should only be given under supervision. Also not more than 1-2 times a week - otherwise cats get used to the smell and lose interest.It is best to keep it outside the playing time in an airtight bag (or wrap well with cling film), so that the scent is preserved for a long time.Colors may vary depending on the device.

name: Mouth protection mask, makeshift mask, makeshift face mask, nose protection, face mask, everyday mask, elastic band, washable
description: Simple and reusable makeshift mask for everyday use.Made entirely of cotton, with elastic bands for wearing and opening for a filter.There are different possibilities for cleaning:Cooking potIf you don't want to start a machine for one or more masks, you can also boil the mask for at least five minutes in a saucepan with water and a pinch of detergent. This is the quick method, so to speak. To determine the correct temperature, you can use a kitchen or grill thermometer. Once the masks are boiled, you should let them dry well.KettlePour hot water from the kettle at a temperature of at least 70 ¬∞C into a pot or heat-resistant bowl. Put the mask in for five minutes, stirring it from time to time with a wooden spoon. Then take it out, lay it out on a towel and let it dry well.These masks are neither a medical product nor protective equipment.Proper handling is therefore important and is strongly recommended.Colors may vary depending on the device.

name: Personalized postcard-sized images. DIN A5 or A4 in retro style
description: Depending on your wishes, I will be able to create a personalized picture for you.Maybe you want to have a picture with grid foil like a classic manga page? A lineart with washitape elements or maybe a mix of both? Everything your heart desires, I can give you a picture that is unique.Raster films/screentones are films that often contain different motifs in black and white and are often used in manga for shadow setting.Washitapes are colorful adhesive tapes with many different sizes and motifs made of rice paper.Depending on the material and size, I offer the following job pictures:Images edited only with raster foil/screentonesA6/ Postcard (105 x 148 mm/4.1 x 5.8 inches)A5 (148 x 210 mm/ 5.8 x 8.3 inches)A4 (210 x 297 mm/ 8.3 x 11.7 inches)Images edited only with WashitapesA6/ Postcard (105 x 148 mm/4.1 x 5.8 inches)A5 (148 x 210 mm/ 5.8 x 8.3 inches)A4 (210 x 297 mm/ 8.3 x 11.7 inches)Images edited with Washitapes and Raster Foil/ScreentonesA6/ Postcard (105 x 148 mm/4.1 x 5.8 inches)A5 (148 x 210 mm/ 5.8 x 8.3 inches)A4 (210 x 297 mm/ 8.3 x 11.7 inches)Write to me which motif you would like to have in this style and I can conjure up something beautiful for you.It is best to give me as many references from the desired motif as possible. If you have any questions, you can contact me at any time.Please clarify your order request in either German or English.Thank you for your purchase.
